n-2-million-military-casualties-in-ukraine-war-report-11715118%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Washington%20DC%20airport%20will%20shut%20down%20for%2015%20hours%20for%20America250%20celebrations%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226144%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22People%20at%20the%20Great%20American%20State%20Fair%20with%20a%20ferris%20wheel%20and%20the%20capitol%20in%20the%20background.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a457a5bec11c5f7e7fa75d4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224608%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Great%20American%20State%20Fair%20runs%20from%20June%2025%20to%20July%2010.%3Cp%3EAlex%20WROBLEWSKI%20%2F%20AFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EReagan%20National%20Airport%20will%20close%20for%2015%20hours%20for%20America250%20celebrations.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAirlines%20adjusted%20schedules%20in%20advance%2C%20and%20the%20airport%20will%20see%20about%20600%20fewer%20flights%20on%20July%204.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20festivities%20include%20flyovers%20by%20B-2%20bombers%20and%20a%20giant%20fireworks%20show.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWashington%20is%20throwing%20a%20party%20for%20America's%20250th%20birthday%20this%20weekend%20that's%20so%20big%20the%20city%20is%20shutting%20down%20a%20major%20airport%20for%20nearly%2015%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Federal%20Aviation%20Administration%20recently%20announced%20that%20Ronald%20Reagan%20Washington%20National%20Airport%2C%20the%20closest%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwashington-national-airport-long-distance-flights-perimeter-rule-faa-capitol-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eairport%20to%20downtown%20Washington%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20D.C.%2C%20will%20close%20from%2010%20a.m.%20to%201%20p.m.%20on%20July%203%20for%20aerial%20rehearsals%2C%20and%20again%20from%20noon%20until%20midnight%20on%20July%204%20for%20the%20Independence%20Day%20celebrations%2C%20which%20include%20military%20flyovers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReagan%20National%20typically%20handles%20about%20850%20flights%20a%20day%2C%20but%20aviation%20analytics%20company%20Cirium%20estimates%20airlines%20have%20scheduled%20only%20260%20flights%20on%20July%204%2C%20roughly%20one-third%20of%20its%20normal%20daily%20traffic.%20Operations%20will%20resume%20on%20July%205.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAirlines%20appear%20to%20have%20received%20months%20of%20notice%2C%20allowing%20them%20to%20trim%20schedules%20rather%20than%20cancel%20flights%20at%20the%20last%20minute%20and%20disrupt%20thousands%20of%20travelers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFlight%20operations%20are%20usually%20paused%20for%20short%20periods%20during%20Washington's%20annual%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjuly-4-party-celebrations-price-hike-tariffs-inflation-sparklers-food-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFourth%20of%20July%3C%2Fa%3E%20fireworks%20show%2C%20sometimes%20forcing%20aircraft%20to%20circle%20until%20the%20airspace%20reopens%20%E2%80%94%20and%20giving%20passengers%20a%20unique%20view%20of%20the%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223111%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22WASHINGTON%2C%20DC%20-%20JUNE%2016%3A%20Water%20in%20the%20Lincoln%20Memorial%20Reflecting%20Pool%20(lower%20right)%20is%20shown%20from%20a%20departing%20flight%20from%20Ronald%20Reagan%20National%20Airport%20as%20algae%20continues%20to%20bloom%20following%20the%20completion%20of%20recent%20renovations%20on%20June%2016%2C%202026%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4578d71aaffe3020cb1e1c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThis%20takeoff%20from%20Reagan%20National%20shows%20how%20close%20the%20flight%20path%20is%20over%20downtown%20DC.%3Cp%3EWin%20McNamee%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20FAA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freagan-airport-delays-fourth-of-july-ground-stops-trump-parade-2019-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estopped%20flights%20at%20Reagan%20National%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20an%20unusually%20long%20two%20hours%20on%20July%204%2C%202019%2C%20during%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20first%20term%2C%20causing%20delays%20and%20cancellations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20a%20nearly%20full%20shutdown%20is%20unprecedented.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20closure%20makes%20way%20for%20the%20gigantic%20airshow%20and%20fireworks%20display%20the%20White%20House%20has%20planned%20for%20Saturday%2C%20including%20flyovers%20by%20Air%20Force%20One%2C%20demonstration%20teams%20like%20the%20US%20Air%20Force%20Thunderbirds%2C%20and%20B-2%20stealth%20bombers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20statements%20to%20Business%20Insider%2C%20American%20Airlines%2C%20Delta%20Air%20Lines%2C%20Southwest%20Airlines%2C%20and%20United%20Airlines%20said%20they%20adjusted%20their%20schedules%20earlier%20this%20year%20to%20account%20for%20the%20closure%20and%20made%20alternate%20flight%20arrangements%20for%20affected%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlaska%20Airlines%2C%20Frontier%20Airlines%2C%20and%20Air%20Canada%2C%20all%20of%20which%20also%20fly%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerican-airlines-adds-new-laguardia-airport-routes-perimeter-rule-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EReagan%20National%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECirium%20data%20shows%20American%2C%20Reagan%20National's%20largest%20airline%2C%20will%20be%20hit%20the%20hardest%20by%20the%20closure%2C%20operating%20about%2050%20fewer%20flights%20than%20usual.%20Other%20carriers%20serving%20the%20airport%20have%20also%20trimmed%20service%20for%20the%20holiday%20weekend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENearby%20Washington%20Dulles%20and%20Baltimore%20airports%20could%20accommodate%20flights%20originally%20destined%20for%20Reagan%20National%2C%20but%20they%2C%20along%20with%20airports%20around%20New%20York%20City%2C%20also%20have%20airs