20to%20stop%20customer%20return%20fraud%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Warehouse%20workers%20checking%20boxes.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a43c961e218c3b62535f297%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAI%20helps%20retailers%20detect%20return%20fraud%2C%20boosting%20efficiency%20in%20reverse%20logistics%20operations.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ERetailers%20employ%20AI%20to%20manage%20high%20return%20volumes%2C%20ensuring%20quicker%20refunds%20and%20customer%20loyalty.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAI%20spots%20unusual%20return%20patterns%2C%20aiding%20in%20fraud%20prevention%20and%20enhancing%20retail%20operations.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20uncommon%20for%20a%20consumer%20to%20order%20the%20same%20shirt%20in%20three%20sizes%2C%20then%20return%20the%20two%20that%20don't%20fit.%20But%20what%20happens%20when%20the%20consumer%20swaps%20the%20labels%20and%20returns%20different%20shirts%2C%20or%20buys%20a%20dress%20for%20an%20event%2C%20wears%20it%20once%20with%20the%20tag%20tucked%20in%2C%20then%20returns%20it%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20are%20examples%20of%20return%20fraud%2C%20a%20retail-industry%20risk%20that's%20on%20the%20rise%20%26quot%3Bin%20both%20scale%20and%20sophistication%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Juan%20Hernandez-Campos%2C%20the%20chief%20operating%20officer%20at%20Happy%20Returns%2C%20a%20software%20company%20that%20manages%20returns%20and%20is%20part%20of%20UPS.%20Today%2C%20about%209%25%20of%20returns%20are%20fraudulent%2C%20according%20to%20the%202025%20Retail%20Returns%20Landscape%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnrf.com%2Fresearch%2F2025-retail-returns-landscape%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereport%20published%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20National%20Retail%20Federation%20and%20Happy%20Returns%20last%20October.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20fraud%20a%20persistent%20problem%20amid%20growing%20return%20volumes%2C%20merchants%20can%20no%20longer%20rely%20on%20the%20%26quot%3Bhighly%20manual%26quot%3B%20methods%20they%20previously%20used%20to%20process%20returns%2C%20Campos%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20retailers%20and%20their%20software%20partners%20are%20turning%20to%20AI%20to%20help%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F9-reverse-logistics-startups-raising-funds-to-tackle-ecommerce-returns-2022-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emanage%20reverse%20logistics%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20part%20of%20the%20supply%20chain%20that%20involves%20handling%20returns%20and%20restocking%20inventory.%20Narvar%2C%20which%20works%20with%20companies%20including%20DSW%20and%20Newell%20Brands%2C%20touts%20AI%20technology%20that%20processes%20billions%20of%20consumer%20data%20points%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freturn-frauds-big-foe-ai-program-that-can-spot-counterfeits-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edetect%20fraud%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Meanwhile%2C%20Loop%20is%20using%20AI%20to%20automate%20decisions%20and%20unearth%20fraud%20for%20customers%20like%20Keen%20and%20Princess%20Polly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJackie%20Swanson%2C%20a%20managing%20partner%20at%20Gartner%20Consulting%2C%20said%20retailers%20have%20shifted%20over%20the%20last%2018%20months%20from%20machine-learning-enhanced%20fraud%20detection%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmastercard-ai-credit-card-fraud-detection-protects-consumers-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eto%20AI%20systems%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20goal%3F%20Stop%20fraud%20in%20its%20tracks%2C%20reduce%20losses%2C%20and%20speed%20up%20legitimate%20returns%2C%20getting%20inventory%20back%20to%20sale%20as%20quickly%20as%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmong%20retailers%20with%20more%20than%20%241%20billion%20in%20annual%20revenue%2C%20%26quot%3Balmost%20all%20of%20them%20have%20something%20in%20place%2C%26quot%3B%20Swanson%20said%2C%20with%20apparel%2C%20beauty%2C%20and%20footwear%20at%20the%20forefront%20due%20to%20their%20high%20return%20rates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22763714d6-b21b-4718-a926-7c3407baa532%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAI%20can%20tackle%20return%20fraud%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECaroline%20Reppert%2C%20the%20senior%20director%20of%20AI%20and%20technology%20policy%20at%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-retail-leaders-said-ai-more-at-nrf-big-show-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENational%20Retail%20Federation%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%20reverse%20logistics%20is%20%26quot%3Bemerging%20as%20a%20key%20focus%20area%26quot%3B%20as%20retailers%20consider%20how%20to%20use%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERetailers%20are%20contending%20with%20return%20fraud%20issues%20like%20overstated%20quantities%20%E2%80%94%20when%20a%20consumer%20claims%20they%20returned%20more%20items%20than%20they%20actually%20did%20%E2%80%94%20empty-box%20returns%2C%20or%20sending%20boxes%20filled%20with%20rocks%2C%20label%20tampering%2C%20and%20counterfeit%20substitutions.%20Some%20consumers%20engage%20in%20wardrobing%2C%20in%20which%20they%20use%20or%20wear%20an%20item%20for%20a%20short%20time%20before%20returning%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20big%20advantage%20of%20AI%2C%20according%20to%20Campos%2C%20is%20that%20it%20can%20analyze%20large%20volumes%20of%20return%20data%20to%20identify%20patterns%20that%20could%20be%20tough%20to%20find%20manually.%20For%20example%2C%20Happy%20Returns%20%E2%80%94%20whose%20clients%20include%20Everlane%2C%20Pact%2C%20and%20Under%20Armour%20%E2%80%94%20uses%20a%20technology%20called%20Return%20Vision%2C%20which%20detects%20discrepancies%20in%20merchandise%20like%20incorrect%20logos%2C%20altered%20tags%2C%20differences%20in%20materials%2C%20or%20product%20swaps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20Return%20Vision%20spots%20one%20of%20these%20issues%2C%20it%20feeds%20the%20data%20to%20retail%20dashboards%20in%20real%20time%2C%20allowing%20retailers%20to%20view%20potential%20problems%20quickly%2C%20Campos%20said.%20Retailers%20can%20see%20why%20the%20return%20was%20flagged%20and%20photos%20of%20the%20returned%20items.%20They%20then%20have%20evidence%20to%20dispute%20any%20consumer%20claims%2C%20even%20before%20the%20item%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-robotics-walmart-distribution-supply-chain-efficiency-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ereaches%20the%20warehouse%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHappy%20Returns%20also%20uses%20AI-based%20behavioral%20risk%20scoring%2C%20which%20identifies%20potentially%20high-risk%20returns%20based%20on%20return%20frequency%2C%20timing%2C%20geography%2C%20and%20historical%20behavior.%20The%20returns%20can%20be%20flagged%20for%20human%20review%20before%20retailers%20issue%20a%20refund.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20retailers%20reveal%20a%20mixed%20picture%20on%20AI%20for%20return%20fraud.%20In%20NRF's%20report%2C%20only%2045%25%20of%20companies%20said%20they%20believe%20AI%20and%20machine%20learning%20are%20truly%20effective%20at%20preventing%20return%20fraud%20on%20their%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBully%20Max%2C%20which%20makes%20dog%20food%20and%20supplements%2C%20uses%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshopify-ceo-tobi-lutke-employees-prove-ai-job-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20systems%20from%20Shopify%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Chargeflow%20to%20detect%20return%20fraud%2C%20according%20to%20CEO%20Matthew%20Kinneman.%20If%20fraud%20occurs%20or%20a%20consumer%20files%20a%20chargeback%2C%20the%20AI%20automatically%20generates%20evidence%20on%20Bully%20Max's%20behalf%20to%20submit%20to%20the%20credit%20card%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20Kinneman%20acknowledged%20that%20AI%20isn't%20perfect.%20The%20company%20has%20to%20manually%20send%20screenshots%20to%20the%20credit%20card%20company%2C%20for%20example.%20%26quot%3BWe've%20found%20that%20human%20review%20is%20still%20essential%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e26db3b1-8b50-4e74-8e00-8f3f6c566ec6%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20speedier%20return%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFraud%20isn't%20the%20only%20use%20case%20for%20AI%20in%20reverse%20logistics.%20Bully%20Max%20also%20uses%20AI%20to%20spot%20patterns%2C%20like%20recurring%20return%20reasons.%20Then%20the%20team%20can%20improve%20a%20product's%20page%20and%20description%2C%20providing%20more%20accurate%20information%20before%20consumers%20make%20a%20purchase.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20many%20cases%2C%20preventing%20a%20return%20is%20more%20valuable%20than%20processing%20one%20efficiently%2C%26quot%3B%20Kinneman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESwanson%20said%20her%20clients%20are%20also%20using%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fartificial-intelligence-robotics-predictive-maintenance-manufacturing-factory-solutions-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20for%20predictive%20returns%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20warehousing%20decisions.%20In%20the%20former%2C%20AI%20models%20proactively%20flag%20orders%20that%20are%20likely%20to%20be%20returned%20and%20suggest%20alternate%20sizes%20or%20products%20before%20the%20consumer%20finalizes%20their%20purchase.%20In%20the%20latter%2C%20when%20a%20return%20arrives%20at%20a%20retailer's%20warehouse%2C%20AI%20recommends%20whether%20the%20retailer%20should%20resell%2C%20liquidate%2C%20or%20even%20destroy%20the%20item%20based%20on%20its%20potential%20resale%20value.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReturns%20have%20historically%20been%20manual%20and%20time-consuming%2C%20Reppert%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20AI%20%26quot%3Ballows%20retailers%20to%20handle%20higher%20return%20volumes%20with%20greater%20speed%20and%20consistency.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdaily-harvest-artificial-intelligence-improve-shipping-and-customer-service-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EFaster%20processing%3C%2Fa%3E%20also%20benefits%20consumers%20by%20providing%20a%20quicker%20refund%20for%20returned%20merchandise%2C%20Campos%20said.%20A%20positive%20return%20experience%20can%20build%20brand%20loyalty%20and%20encourage%20consumers%20to%20make%20another%20purchase%20with%20the%20retailer%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freturn-fraud-ai-retail-happy-returns-optoro-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1782930791000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a43c961e218c3b62535f297%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freturn-fraud-ai-retail-happy-returns-optoro-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Retailers%20are%20implementing%20AI%20through%20software%20companies%20like%20Happy%20Returns%20and%20Narvar%20to%20detect%20return%20fraud%20and%20issue%20refunds%20more%20quickly.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Shefali%20Kapadia)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Trump's%20new%20Air%20Force%20One%2C%20a%20luxury%20jet%20from%20Qatar%2C%20compares%20to%20the%20outgoing%20presidential%20plane%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20old%20and%20new%20Air%20Force%20One%20planes.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a44260ba25092c74cca1b1d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20old%20and%20new%20Air%20Force%20One%20planes.%3Cp%3EGustavo%20Valiente%2FEuropa%20Press%20via%20Getty%20Images%20%3B%20Andrew%20Leyden%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump%20flew%20on%20his%20new%20Air%20Force%20One%20for%20the%20first%20time%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20VC-25B%2C%20a%20luxury%20jet%20valued%20at%20around%20%24400%20million%2C%20was%20gifted%20to%20Trump%20by%20Qatar.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20new%20Air%20Force%20One%20is%20bigger%2C%20faster%2C%20more%20fuel-efficient%2C%20and%20more%20luxurious%20than%20the%20old%20one.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20his%20first%20term%20in%20the%20White%20House%2C%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20has%20displayed%20a%20model%20of%20a%20new%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fair-force-one-photos-through-history-2021-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAir%20Force%20One%3C%2Fa%3E%20plane%20on%20his%20desk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20his%20long-held%20vision%20became%20a%20reality%20when%20the%20aircraft%20he%20accepted%20as%20a%20gift%20from%20Qatar%2C%20designated%20the%20VC-25B%20Bridge%2C%20flew%20as%20Air%20Force%20One%20for%20the%20first%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20reporters%20before%20boarding%20the%20aircraft%20at%20Joint%20Base%20Andrews%20in%20Maryland%2C%20Trump%20called%20it%20the%20%26quot%3Bbest%20plane%20ever%20built.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20later%20landed%20in%20Medora%2C%20North%20Dakota%2C%20for%20the%20dedication%20of%20the%20Theodore%20Roosevelt%20Presidential%20Library.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERetrofitted%20with%20state-of-the-art%20protective%20measures%20and%20painted%20with%20his%20favored%20colors%20of%20red%2C%20white%2C%20and%20blue%2C%20the%20new%20presidential%20plane%20is%20bigger%2C%20faster%2C%20more%20fuel-efficient%2C%20and%20more%20luxurious%20than%20the%20outgoing%20VC-25A%2C%20which%20has%20been%20in%20service%20since%20President%20George%20H.W.%20Bush%20held%20office%20in%20the%201990s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20how%20Trump's%20new%20VC-25B%20Bridge%20compares%20to%20the%20old%20VC-25A.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20old%20Air%20Force%20One%20was%20a%20customized%20Boeing%20747-200B%2C%20designated%20VC-25A%2C%20that%20entered%20service%20under%20President%20George%20H.W.%20Bush.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22President%20George%20Bush%20and%20first%20lady%20Barbara%20Bush%20exit%20Air%20Force%20One%20in%201991.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4429f6360acd489560dc83%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPresident%20George%20Bush%20and%20first%20lady%20Barbara%20Bush%20exit%20Air%20Force%20One%20in%201991.%3Cp%3EShepard%20Sherbell%2FCorbis%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20VC-25A%2C%20known%20as%20SAM%2028000%2C%20began%20serving%20as%20Air%20Force%20One%20in%201990.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20outgoing%20Air%20Force%20One%2C%20a%20second%2C%20identical%20VC-25A%20known%20as%20SAM%2029000%2C%20entered%20service%20in%201991.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20VC-25A%20measures%20231%20feet%20and%2010%20inches%20long%20with%20a%20wingspan%20of%20195%20feet%20and%208%20inches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20new%20Air%20Force%20One%20is%20a%20customized%20Boeing%20747-8i%20built%20in%202012%20and%20previously%20used%20as%20a%20luxury%20transport%20by%20the%20Qatari%20royal%20family.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Qatari%20Boeing%20747.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a442a54e218c3b62535f92e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIn%20this%20February%2015%2C%202025%20a%20Qatari%20Boeing%20747%20sits%20on%20the%20tarmac%20of%20Palm%20Beach%20International%20airport%20after%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20toured%20the%20aircraft%20on%20February%2015%2C%202025.%20Donald%20Trump%20plans%20to%20accept%20a%20luxury%20Boeing%20jet%20from%20the%20Qatari%20royal%20family%20for%20use%20as%20Air%20Force%20One%20and%20then%20continue%20flying%20in%20it%20after%20his%20tenure%2C%20despite%20strict%20rules%20on%20US%20presidential%20gifts%2C%20media%20reported%20May%2011%2C%202025.%20Calling%20the%20plane%20a%20%26quot%3Bflying%20palace%2C%26quot%3B%20ABC%20News%2C%20which%20first%20reported%20the%20story%2C%20said%20the%20Boeing%20747-8%20jumbo%20jet%20would%20possibly%20be%20the%20most%20expensive%20gift%20ever%20received%20by%20the%20American%20government.%3Cp%3EROBERTO%20SCHMIDT%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20VC-25B%20Bridge%20%E2%80%94%20so%20called%20because%20it's%20serving%20as%20an%20interim%20presidential%20aircraft%20before%20Boeing's%20customized%20VC-25Bs%20are%20completed%20in%202027%20or%202028%20%E2%80%94%20is%20larger%20than%20the%20VC-25A%20at%20250%20feet%20long%2C%20with%20a%20wingspan%20of%20224%20feet%20and%205%20inches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20old%20Air%20Force%20One%20featured%20a%20light%20blue%20and%20white%20paint%20job%20resembling%20the%20design%20originally%20chosen%20by%20first%20lady%20Jacqueline%20Kennedy.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22SAM%2029000.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a442aaaa25092c74cca1b66%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAir%20Force%20One%20transporting%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20from%20Joint%20Base%20Andrews%2C%20Maryland%2C%20to%20attend%20the%20NATO%20summit%20in%20The%20Hague%2C%20lands%20at%20Amsterdam's%20Schiphol%20aiport%20on%20June%2024%2C%202025.%20NATO%20leaders%20hold%20a%20two-day%20summit%20on%20June%2024%20and%2025%20in%20The%20Hague.%20(Photo%20by%20Koen%20van%20Weel%20%2F%20ANP%20%2F%20AFP)%20%2F%20Netherlands%20OUT%20(Photo%20by%20KOEN%20VAN%20WEEL%2FANP%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3Cp%3EKoen%20van%20Weel%2FANP%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EJacqueline%20Kennedy%20chose%20the%20shades%20of%20blue%20and%20white%20for%20SAM%2026000%2C%20a%20Boeing%20VC-137C%20that%20entered%20service%20in%201962%20under%20President%20John%20F.%20Kennedy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20lady%20was%20also%20responsible%20for%20adding%20the%20words%20%26quot%3BUnited%20States%20of%20America%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fair-force-one-plane-tour-sam-26000-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epresidential%20plane%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20American%20flag%20was%20featured%20on%20the%20tail%2C%20with%20the%20stars%20facing%20forward%20per%20the%20US%20Flag%20Code.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ETrump%20selected%20a%20red%2C%20white%2C%20and%20navy%20blue%20livery%20for%20the%20new%20Air%20Force%20One%20and%20a%20new%20waving%20American%20flag%20design%20on%20the%20tail.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Trump's%20new%20Air%20Force%20One%20jet.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4421abe218c3b62535f88e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJOINT%20BASE%20ANDREWS%2C%20MARYLAND%20-%20JUNE%2022%3A%20A%20Boeing%20747-8%20jetliner%20practices%20touch%20and%20go%20landings%20on%20June%2022%2C%202026%20in%20Joint%20Base%20Andrews%2C%20Maryland.%20The%20plane%2C%20which%20was%20a%20gift%20from%20the%20government%20of%20Qatar%2C%20is%20designated%20as%20the%20new%20Air%20Force%20One%20and%20will%20replace%20the%20military-grade%20747-2.%20The%20Air%20Force%20has%20been%20working%20to%20upgrade%20the%20jet%20so%20it%20is%20ready%20for%20presidential%20transport.%3Cp%3EAndrew%20Leyden%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.af.mil%2FNews%2FArticle-Display%2FArticle%2F3326103%2Fnew-paint-design-for-next-air-force-one%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAir%20Force%3C%2Fa%3E%20initially%20rejected%20the%20navy%20paint%20color%20Trump%20proposed%20during%20his%20first%20term%20for%20the%20forthcoming%20VC-25Bs%2C%20saying%20a%20thermal%20study%20found%20that%20the%20darker%20shade%20would%20require%20additional%20testing%20to%20avoid%20overheating%20issues.%20However%2C%20Trump%20got%20his%20preferred%20colors%20in%20his%20second%20term.%20He%20also%20reimagined%20the%20tail's%20flag%20design.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20you%20know%2C%20we've%20always%20gone%20with%20a%20straight%20little%20noodle%20and%20I%20never%20loved%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said%20of%20the%20tail's%20new%20waving%20flag%20design%20after%20touring%20the%20plane%20at%20Joint%20Base%20Andrews%20on%20June%2019.%20%26quot%3BNow%20we%20have%20a%20wavy%2C%20beautiful%20flag.%20We're%20waving%20it%20proudly%20because%20our%20country%20is%20doing%20so%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20old%20Air%20Force%20One%20jet%20had%20four%20General%20Electric%20CF6-80C2B1%20jet%20engines%2C%20each%20with%2056%2C700%20pounds%20of%20thrust.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Air%20Force%20One%2C%20SAM%2029000.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a442e1de218c3b62535f96e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221687%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump%20arrives%20at%20the%20Kentucky%20Air%20National%20Guard%20Base%20in%20Louisville%2C%20Ky.%2C%20aboard%20Air%20Force%20One%20on%20Aug.%2021%2C%202019.%20Trump%20was%20in%20town%20to%20speak%20at%20an%20AMVETS%20convention%20and%20attend%20a%20fundraiser%20for%20Kentucky%20Gov.%20Matt%20Bevin's%20re-election%20campaign.%3Cp%3EUS%20Air%20National%20Guard%20photo%20by%20Dale%20Greer%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20traveling%20at%20630%20miles%20per%20hour%2C%20the%20VC-25A%20had%20a%20range%20of%207%2C800%20miles%20without%20refueling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20four%20GEnx-2B%20engines%20on%20the%20new%20Air%20Force%20One%20each%20feature%2066%2C500%20pounds%20of%20thrust%20and%20emit%2016%20tons%20less%20carbon%20dioxide%20per%20trip%2C%20the%20White%20House%20said.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20four%20engines%20on%20the%20new%20Air%20Force%20One.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4421dce218c3b62535f896%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJOINT%20BASE%20ANDREWS%2C%20MARYLAND%20-%20JUNE%2022%3A%20A%20Boeing%20747-8%20jetliner%20practices%20touch%20and%20go%20landings%20on%20June%2022%2C%202026%20in%20Joint%20Base%20Andrews%2C%20Maryland.%20The%20plane%2C%20which%20was%20a%20gift%20from%20the%20government%20of%20Qatar%2C%20is%20designated%20as%20the%20new%20Air%20Force%20One%20and%20will%20replace%20the%20military-grade%20747-2.%20The%20Air%20Force%20has%20been%20working%20to%20upgrade%20the%20jet%20so%20it%20is%20ready%20for%20presidential%20transport.%3Cp%3EAndrew%20Leyden%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20VC-25B%20Bridge%20can%20fly%20faster%20and%20farther%20than%20its%20predecessor%2C%20with%20a%20range%20of%208%2C900%20miles%20at%20660%20miles%20per%20hour.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20the%20VC-25A%20and%20VC-25B%20Bridge%20are%20capable%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fair-force-aerial-refueling-tanker-kc-10a-extender-tour-photos-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emidair%20refueling%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20interiors%20of%20the%20old%20Air%20Force%20One%20largely%20remained%20the%20same%20through%20several%20administrations%2C%20with%20a%20few%20cosmetic%20changes.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Trump%20on%20Air%20Force%20One.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a453aa91aaffe3020cb118d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20Chief%20of%20Staff%20Susie%20Wiles%2C%20and%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Marco%20Rubio%20meet%20with%20Qatar's%20Emir%20Sheikh%20Tamim%20bin%20Hamad%20Al-Thani%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20and%20Foreign%20Minister%20Sheikh%20Mohammed%20bin%20Abdulrahman%20bin%20Jassim%20Al-Thani%20aboard%20Air%20Force%20One%20during%20a%20refueling%20stop%20in%20Doha%2C%20Qatar%2C%20enroute%20to%20the%20ASEAN%20summit%20in%20Malaysia%2C%20October%2025%2C%202025.%3Cp%3EOfficial%20White%20House%20Photo%20by