5C%222400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Steve%20Cohen%20in%20a%20Mets%20hat%20looks%20to%20the%20side%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a45446b2680585ce91a31e7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221601%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBillionaire%20Point72%20founder%20Steve%20Cohen%20also%20owns%20the%20New%20York%20Mets.%3Cp%3EAlejandra%20Villa%20Loarca%2FNewsday%20RM%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EHalfway%20through%202026%2C%20big-name%20hedge%20funds%20have%20mostly%20performed%20well.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EManagers%20like%20Millennium%20and%20Point72%20benefited%20from%20a%20resurgent%20stock%20market%20in%20the%20second%20quarter.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EFew%20managers%20can%20match%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20index's%20nearly%2010%25%20return%20through%20the%20year's%20first%20half%2C%20though.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20blockbuster%20quarter%20for%20equities%20helped%20fuel%20strong%20returns%20from%20big-name%20hedge%20funds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThrough%20the%20first%20six%20months%20of%202026%2C%20the%20most%20closely%20watched%20space%20in%20the%20industry%20%E2%80%94%20the%20large-scale%20multistrategy%20managers%20such%20as%20Millennium%2C%20Point72%2C%20and%20Schonfeld%20%E2%80%94%20has%20performed%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20some%20highlights%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EPoint72%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20returned%203.4%25%20in%20June%2C%20pushing%20Steve%20Cohen's%20firm's%20first-half%20returns%20to%2014.5%25%2C%20a%20person%20close%20to%20the%20manager%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EMillennium%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20is%20up%2010.5%25%20for%202026's%20first%20six%20months%2C%20a%20person%20close%20to%20the%20fund%20told%20Business%20Insider%2C%20after%20a%20gain%20of%204.1%25%20in%20June.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ESchonfeld%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eposted%20a%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E2.5%25%20gain%20in%20June%2C%20bringing%20the%20manager's%20flagship%20to%208.4%25%20for%20the%20first%20half%20of%20the%20year.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EInvestors%20began%20pricing%20in%20an%20Iran-war%20resolution%20at%20the%20very%20end%20of%20March.%20The%20result%20was%20a%20market%20bottom%20that%20lined%20up%20perfectly%20with%20the%20start%20of%20a%20new%20quarter.%20The%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-today-dow-sp500-nasdaq-record-ai-026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Erose%2015%25%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20period%2C%20while%20the%20tech-heavy%20Nasdaq%20100%20surged%2028%25.%20Not%20to%20mention%2C%20SpaceX%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspacex-ipo-spcx-stock-price-stocks-investing-elon-musk-nasdaq-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estarted%20trading%20publicly%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20the%20biggest%20IPO%20in%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20finished%20the%20first%20half%20of%202026%20up%20close%20to%2010%25.%20While%20that's%20outpaced%20most%20hedge%20funds%2C%20some%20managers'%20equity-only%20options%20have%20outperformed.%20%3Cstrong%3ESchonfeld's%20Fundamental%20Equities%20fund%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20for%20example%2C%20is%20up%2012.3%25%20in%20the%20first%20half%20after%20a%203.6%25%20gain%20last%20month%2C%20a%20person%20close%20to%20the%20manager%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20funds%20mentioned%20declined%20to%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBelow%20is%20the%20full%20scorecard.%20Funds%20will%20be%20added%20as%20their%20returns%20are%20learned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ctable%3E%3Ccolgroup%3E%3Ccol%3E%3Ccol%3E%3Ccol%3E%3C%2Fcolgroup%3E%3Ctbody%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%3E%3Cstrong%3EFund%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E%3Cstrong%3EJune%20performance%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E%3Cstrong%3E2026%20performance%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%20colspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20rowspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EPinpoint%20Asset%20Management%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%20colspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20rowspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3E4.4%25%3C%2Ftd%3