0data%20centers%20is%20held%20during%20a%20protest%20against%20AI%20data%20centers%20in%20Canada%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a45296eec11c5f7e7fa690f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EBloomberg%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EVenture%20capitalist%20Vijay%20Pande%20says%20that%20everyone%20should%20be%20rooting%20for%20the%20AI%20bubble%20to%20burst.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20said%20a%20crash%20is%20is%20necessary%20to%20move%20the%20market%20forward.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHis%20forecast%20is%20based%20on%20a%20bubble%20he%20sees%20developing%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20trajectory%20of%20past%20bubbles.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20venture%20capitalists%20probably%20don't%20root%20for%20the%20hottest%20investment%20theme%20of%20the%20current%20era%20to%20flame%20out%20and%20crash.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fvijaypande%2Fstatus%2F2071943432709558343%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epost%20on%20X%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20June%2030%2C%20Vijay%20Pande%2C%20founder%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2FVZ.VC%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVZ.VC%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20laid%20out%20why%20he's%20rooting%20for%20the%20AI-fueled%20investing%20bubble%20to%20burst.%20More%20than%20that%2C%20he%20argued%20that%20everyone%20should%20feel%20this%20way%2C%20making%20a%20case%20for%20why%20the%20bursting%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-bubble-sp500-valuations-tech-dot-com-seth-bernstein-ceo-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20AI%20bubble%3C%2Fa%3E%20could%20be%20the%20best%20thing%20for%20the%20broader%20economy%20in%20the%20longterm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20telling%20you%20to%20root%20for%20the%20crash%20that%20torches%20my%20own%20asset%20class%2C%26quot%3B%20Pande%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BI%20mean%20it.%20The%20valuations%20are%20silly%2C%20the%20data-center%20spending%20is%20feverish%2C%20and%20half%20the%20people%20I%20talk%20to%20are%20quietly%20bracing%20for%20the%20fall.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPande%20said%20that%20he%20thinks%20a%20stock%20market%20crash%20is%20inevitable%20at%20this%20point%2C%20but%20when%20it%20happens%2C%20it%20will%20ultimately%20prove%20to%20be%20a%20positive%20development.%20A%20reversal%20of%20AI%20mania%2C%20he%20argues%2C%20is%20necessary%20for%20a%20%26quot%3BRenaissance%20cycle%26quot%3B%20of%20growth%20and%20rebuilding%20that%20comes%20with%20the%20disruption%20prompted%20by%20a%20new%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20highlighted%20an%20analysis%20from%20economist%20Carlota%20Perez%2C%20who%20said%20that%20every%20significant%20technology%20surge%20of%20the%20past%20250%20years%20followed%20the%20same%20trajectory.%20They%20began%20with%20a%20revolution%2C%20followed%20by%20a%20financial%20bubble%2C%20a%20market%20collapse%2C%20and%2C%20ultimately%2C%20a%20golden%20age.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPande%20pointed%20not%20just%20to%20the%20rise%20of%20things%20like%20cars%20and%20computers%2C%20but%20canals%2C%20railways%2C%20and%20steel%20production.%20Others%2C%20too%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-bubble-ai-valuations-nvidia-broadcom-dot-com-crash-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehave%20compared%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20AI%20surge%20to%20the%20dot-com%20bubble%20that%20sparked%20the%20crash%20of%20the%20early%202000s%2C%20which%20in%20turn%20gave%20way%20to%20a%20new%20generation%20of%20innovation%20and%20market%20expansion.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20living%20through%20the%20same%20process%20now%2C%20except%20the%20rails%20of%20today%20are%20compute%2C%20data%20centers%2C%20models%2C%20and%20the%20habit%20of%20millions%20of%20people%20learning%20to%20think%20alongside%20a%20machine%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20chips%20will%20depreciate%2C%20sure%2C%20but%20the%20chips%20were%20never%20the%20rail%3B%20the%20power%2C%20the%20grid%20hookups%2C%20the%20data-center%20shells%2C%20and%20a%20generation%20that%20learned%20to%20work%20with%20machines%20are.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20memory%20chips%20that%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-memory-chip-boom-next-trillion-dollar-company-sk-hynix-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epowering%20the%20AI%20boom%3C%2Fa%3E%20may%20not%20survive%20a%20stock%20market%20crash%2C%20but%20in%20Pande's%20view%2C%20durable%20infrastructure%20and%20human%20habit%20of%20learning%20to%20work%20with%20AI%20will%20be%20the%20real%20lasting%20development%2C%20proving%20valuable%20when%20the%20US%20begins%20rebuilding%20after%20the%20crash.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20scenario%20he%20sees%20unfolding%20is%20one%20in%20which%20the%20stock%20market%20crash%20%26quot%3Bfinishes%20the%20build%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3Bsobers%20the%20money%26quot%3B%20by%20discouraging%20the%20high%20spending%20that%20created%20the%20bubble%2C%20and%20ultimately%2C%20forces%20the%20rebuild%20in%20which%20people%20figure%20out%20how%20to%20properly%20live%20with%20the%20technology.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20bubble%20and%20the%20crash%20that%20ends%20it%20are%20not%20a%20detour%20around%20the%20golden%20age%2C%26quot%3B%20Pande%20added.%20%26quot%3BThey%20are%20the%20road%20to%20it.%20But%20if%20done%20wrong%2C%20the%20same%20turning%20point%20that%20built%20the%20American%20suburbs%20built%20the%20gulag.%20The%20only%20variable%20is%20how%20we%20respond.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-bubble-stock-market-crash-venture-capital-economy-vijay-pande-2026-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1782924888000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4529781aaffe3020cb0972%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-bubble-stock-market-crash-venture-capital-economy-vijay-pande-2026-7%22%2C%22summary