nID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdeloitte-digital-mark-singer-cmo-cannes-lions-2026-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Successful%20CMOs%20need%20to%20be%20entrepreneurial%20and%20comfortable%20with%20ambiguity%2C%20said%20Mark%20Singer%20of%20Deloitte%20Digital.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jhood%40businessinsider.com%20(Julia%20Hood)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20engineer%20who%20became%20Anthropic's%20political%20secret%20weapon%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Anthropic%20cofounder%20Tom%20Brown.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a44d9daa25092c74cca1df2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAnthropic%20cofounder%20Tom%20Brown.%3Cp%3EReuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ETom%20Brown%20mediated%20Anthropic's%20standoff%20with%20the%20U.S.%20over%20AI%20models%20Fable%205%20and%20Mythos%205.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBrown%20is%20less%20well%20known%20than%20several%20of%20his%20Anthropic%20cofounders%2C%20despite%20his%20major%20achievements.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHis%20journey%20to%20the%20closely%20watched%20White%20House%20negotiation%20wound%20through%20startups%20and%20OpenAI.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Anthropic%20found%20itself%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdario-amodei-ai-warnings-mythos-fable-blocked-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehigh-stakes%20standoff%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewith%20the%20White%20House%20over%20its%20newest%20AI%20models%2C%20it%20wasn't%20CEO%20Dario%20Amodei%20who%20smoothed%20the%20tensions.%20Instead%2C%20one%20of%20the%20company's%20quietest%20cofounders%20stepped%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETom%20Brown%2C%20Anthropic's%20chief%20compute%20officer%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wired.com%2Fstory%2Fthe-trump-white-house-is-over-anthropics-dario-amodei%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehelped%20negotiate%20a%20deal%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20persuaded%20the%20Commerce%20Department%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-restores-fable-5-mythos-access-trump-white-house-talks-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elift%20export%20restrictions%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20company's%20newest%20flagship%20models%2C%20Fable%205%20and%20Mythos%205.%20The%20episode%20thrust%20one%20of%20AI's%20least%20visible%20leaders%20into%20the%20spotlight%20%E2%80%94%20and%20revealed%20how%20the%20engineer%20responsible%20for%20securing%20Anthropic's%20computing%20power%20has%20become%20one%20of%20its%20most%20important%20diplomats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20proved%20to%20be%20a%20win%20for%20the%20under-the-radar%20cofounder.%20Brown%20hasn't%20received%20the%20same%20media%20spotlight%20as%20his%20peers%2C%20but%20in%20finding%20the%20chips%20to%20power%20the%20company's%20AI%20technology%2C%20he%20leads%20an%20indispensable%20part%20of%20its%20grandiose%20ambitions.%20These%20recent%20White%20House%20negotiations%20show%20that%20his%20value%20extends%20to%20the%20political%20arena%2C%20where%20he's%20served%20well%20by%20his%20knack%20for%20relationships%20and%20straightforwardness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMichael%20Waxman%2C%20who%20cofounded%20a%20dating%20startup%20with%20Brown%20in%20the%202010s%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20he's%20generally%20been%20very%20optimistic%20about%20AI%2C%20but%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BKnowing%20Tom's%20character%20and%20that%20he's%20in%20the%20room%20at%20the%20leading%20edge%20of%20some%20of%20these%20really%20important%20decisions%20definitely%20makes%20me%20just%20feel%20better%20and%20sleep%20easier%20at%20night.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnthropic's%20head%20of%20public%20policy%2C%20Sarah%20Heck%2C%20worked%20alongside%20Brown%20on%20the%20White%20House%20talks%2C%20but%20US%20Commerce%20Secretary%20Howard%20Lutnick%20addressed%20his%20Tuesday%20letter%20about%20the%20export%20controls%20directly%20to%20Brown%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wired.com%2Fstory%2Ftrump-administration-lifts-export-controls-on-anthropics-mythos-and-fable-ai-models%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWired%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%20Here%20are%20some%20key%20things%20to%20know%20about%20the%2039-year-old%20cofounder's%20background.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f8fbaf7a-1730-424f-bbf9-259141656e80%5C%22%3EBrown%20bounced%20around%20Silicon%20Valley's%20startup%20world%20before%20teaching%20himself%20AI%20research%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOut%20of%20college%20at%20MIT%2C%20Brown%20jumped%20into%20the%20Silicon%20Valley%20scene.%20He%20worked%20as%20an%20early%20employee%20at%20the%20language-teaching%20startup%20Lingt%2C%20went%20briefly%20back%20to%20school%2C%20then%20worked%20at%20the%20mobile%20advertising%20startup%20MoPub.%20He%20then%20cofounded%20Grouper%2C%20a%20startup%20that%20matched%20pairs%20of%20trios%20for%20in-person%20meetups%2C%20with%20Waxman%20as%20part%20of%20the%20accelerator%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-y-combinator-founders-are-pitching-the-ai-boom-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EY%20Combinator%3C%2Fa%3E's%20winter%202012%20batch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWaxman%20said%20in%20those%20days%2C%20Brown%20had%20all%20the%20%26quot%3Btable%20stakes%26quot%3B%20of%20a%20leader%20%E2%80%94%20%26quot%3Bgood%20human%2C%20kind%2C%20high%20integrity%2C%20always%20truthful%2C%20direct%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that%20he%20also%20managed%20to%20build%20bridges%20across%20discipline%20divides%20within%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrown%20left%20a%20struggling%20Grouper%20after%20a%20few%20years%20and%20then%20decided%20to%20pivot.%20He%20said%20on%20YC's%20Lightcone%20Podcast%20last%20year%20that%20at%20the%20time%2C%20he%20didn't%20have%20the%20skills%20to%20jump%20into%20AI%20research%2C%20so%20he%20kicked%20off%20a%20monthslong%20self-study%20sprint%3A%20a%20Coursera%20course%2C%20Kaggle%20projects%2C%20and%20the%20book%20%26quot%3BLinear%20Algebra%20Done%20Right.%26quot%3B%20He%20even%20bought%20a%20GPU%20chip%20with%20YC%20credits%2C%20he%20said%2C%20to%20work%20through%20his%20courses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWaxman%20remembers%20Brown%20asking%20him%20to%20join%20a%20machine-learning%20study%20group%20in%202015.%20He%20shrugged%20off%20Brown's%20invite%20%E2%80%94%20not%20knowing%20his%20old%20cofounder%20was%20learning%20enough%20to%20later%20transform%20the%20entire%20field.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223d46ce95-f357-4e5b-b619-ede23717d7a5%5C%22%3EGreg%20Brockman%20helped%20Brown%20get%20his%20foot%20in%20the%20door%20at%20OpenAI%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGrouper%20ultimately%20lost%20out%20to%20Tinder%20and%20other%20swipe-based%20dating%20apps.%20But%20the%20startup%20had%20gained%20one%20major%20fan%3A%20then-chief%20technical%20officer%20at%20Stripe%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-greg-brockman-political-donations-super-pac-statement-leading-future-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGreg%20Brockman%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Brown%20said%20on%20the%20Lightcone%20Podcast%20that%2C%20during%20one%20stretch%2C%20Brockman%20would%20set%20up%20Grouper%20meetings%20as%20often%20as%20once%20a%20week%2C%20and%20the%20two%20got%20to%20know%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20end%20of%202015%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-trial-greg-brockman-testimony-elon-musk-breakup-compute-costs-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBrockman%20cofounded%20OpenAI%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20a%20small%20crew%20of%20researchers%20and%20engineers%20%E2%80%94%20the%20first%20office%20was%20his%20apartment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20messaged%20Greg%20as%20soon%20as%20OpenAI%20was%20announced%2C%20and%20I%20was%20like%2C%20'I'd%20love%20to%20help%20out%20in%20some%20way.%20I%20got%20a%20B-%20in%20linear%20algebra%2C%20but%20I%20know%20some%20engineering.%20I've%20done%20a%20bit%20of%20distributed%20systems%20work%20if%20you%20guys%20need%20help.%20I'm%20happy%20to%20mop%20floors%20if%20you%20guys%20need%20me%20to.%20I%20want%20to%20help%20out%20however%2C'%26quot%3B%20Brown%20recalled.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrockman%20eventually%20gave%20Brown%20a%20job%20on%20a%20project%20related%20to%20the%20game%20%26quot%3BStarCraft.%26quot%3B%20Brown%20didn't%20do%20machine%20learning%20work%20for%20his%20first%20nine%20months%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%202024%20video%20discussion%20with%20Anthropic's%20cofounders%2C%20Brown%20recalled%20being%20drawn%20to%20OpenAI%20by%20the%20idea%20that%2C%20as%20an%20engineer%2C%20he%20could%20help%20advance%20AI%20safety%20%E2%80%94%20a%20field%20that%20had%20previously%20seemed%20reserved%20for%20researchers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2276166cf3-b22d-4e1e-a782-0f952230355f%5C%22%3EBrown%20worked%20on%20multiple%20blockbuster%20papers%20of%20the%20AI%20era%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBrown%20wasn't%20originally%20a%20researcher.%20Now%2C%20his%20Google%20Scholar%20page%20lists%20more%20than%20140%2C000%20citations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20one%20of%20six%20authors%20from%20OpenAI%20and%20DeepMind%20on%20a%20seminal%202017%20paper%20that%20paved%20the%20way%20for%20Reinforcement%20Learning%20from%20Human%20Feedback%2C%20a%20cornerstone%20of%20modern%20AI%20training.%20After%20leaving%20for%20a%20stint%20at%20Google%2C%20Brown%20returned%20to%20OpenAI%20in%202018%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eand%20helped%20push%20the%20field%20toward%20its%20eventual%20boom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20more%20bombshells%20landed%20in%202020.%20Brown%20helped%20with%20%26quot%3BScaling%20Laws%20for%20Neural%20Language%20Models%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20this%20paper%20established%20the%20%26quot%3Bscaling%20laws%26quot%3B%20that%20have%20driven%20frontier%20AI%20developers%20to%20build%20ever-bigger%20models%2C%20forecasting%20performance%20improvements%20over%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20later%20in%20the%20year%2C%20came%20%26quot%3BLanguage%20Models%20are%20Few-Shot%20Learners.%26quot%3B%20Brown%20was%20a%20main%20author%2C%20having%20led%20the%20research's%20engineering%20effort.%20The%20paper%20introduced%20the%20large%20language%20model%20GPT-3%2C%20marking%20a%20major%20turning%20point%20in%20the%20industry%20toward%20training%20bigger%20models%20and%20using%20prompts%20to%20control%20them.%20It%20would%20serve%20as%20the%20foundation%20for%20ChatGPT.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrown%20said%20on%20the%20Lightcone%20Podcast%20that%20it%20was%20OpenAI's%20scaling%20and%20safety%20teams%20%E2%80%94%20who%20reported%20to%20Daniela%20and%20Dario%20Amodei%20while%20at%20OpenAI%20%E2%80%94%20that%20seemed%20to%20take%20the%20%26quot%3Bscaling%20law%26quot%3B%20idea%20most%20seriously.%20He%20said%20the%20group%20thought%20there%20would%20be%20a%20time%20%26quot%3Bwhere%20humanity%20will%20hand%20off%20control%20to%20transformative%20AI%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20they%20wanted%20to%20be%20sure%20the%20stakes%20were%20taken%20seriously%20enough.%20That%20group%20cofounded%20Anthropic%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e3ff48be-5f53-449d-aad2-cfd21bdb1e8e%5C%22%3EBrown%20leads%20Anthropic's%20high-stakes%20compute%20push%20%E2%80%94%20a%20job%20that%20demands%20constant%20cooperation%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20AI%20executives%20can%20hunker%20down%20within%20their%20companies%2C%20focusing%20on%20research%20bets%20or%20product%20iterations.%20Brown%20is%20forced%20to%20haggle%20with%20some%20of%20the%20biggest%20power%20players%20in%20the%20corporate%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20bid%20to%20secure%20enough%20computing%20power%20to%20train%20and%20run%20its%20models%2C%20Anthropic's%20compute%20team%2C%20led%20by%20Brown%2C%20has%20struck%20deals%20across%20the%20industry.%20The%20company%20uses%20Amazon's%20Trainium%20chips%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-skips-one-of-silicon-valleys-oldest-traditions-free-food-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENvidia's%20GPUs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20Google's%20TPUs%2C%20routing%20different%20tasks%20to%20different%20chips%20and%20benefiting%20from%20access%20to%20a%20broader%20range.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20spring%2C%20when%20Anthropic%20was%20feeling%20a%20compute%20crunch%20amid%20rabid%20demand%20for%20its%20Claude%20Code%20product%2C%20Brown%20and%20his%20team%20announced%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspacex-ipo-anthropic-paying-ai-compute-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emultibillion-dollar%20deal%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20run%20Anthropic's%20models%20on%20SpaceX's%20huge%20data%20center%2C%20Colossus.%20Brown%20has%20also%20spoken%20on%20behalf%20of%20Anthropic%20at%20Amazon%20Web%20Services'%20re%3A%20Invent%20conference%2C%20and%20was%20quoted%20in%20a%202023%20Google%20Cloud%20release%20hyping%20up%20an%20AI%20infrastructure%20collaboration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202024%20discussion%20with%20his%20cofounders%2C%20Brown%20said%20that%20during%20his%20work%20on%20compute%2C%20he%20talks%20with%20some%20people%20who%20haven't%20come%20around%20to%20his%20view%20that%20AI%20will%20be%20so%20rapidly%20transformative.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20started%20out%20not%20thinking%20stuff%20would%20be%20that%20fast%2C%20and%20have%20changed%20over%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20I%20have%20sympathy%20for%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2215c0fa20-93eb-41a8-8e56-722d589d9ff2%5C%22%3ELike%20Anthropic's%20other%20cofounders%2C%20Brown%20has%20pledged%20to%20donate%20most%20of%20his%20massive%20wealth%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBloomberg%20estimates%20that%20Brown's%20net%20worth%20is%20nearly%20%248%20billion%2C%20thanks%20entirely%20to%20his%20Anthropic%20stake%20and%20the%20company's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-surpasses-openai-with-965b-valuation-debuts-opus-4-8-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%24965%20billion%20valuation.%3C%2Fa%3E%20And%20he%2C%20like%20many%20of%20his%20cofounders%2C%20has%20pledged%20to%20give%20away%2080%25%20of%20his%20wealth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rollback%20of%20the%20White%20House's%20restrictions%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20cooling%20of%20tensions%20that%20the%20move%20implies%20%E2%80%94%20comes%20at%20a%20crucial%20time%20for%20Anthropic.%20The%20startup%20is%20eyeing%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-submits-s-1-joins-ipo-race-with-openai-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Einitial%20public%20offering%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethat%20would%20provide%20employees%20with%20a%20liquidity%20event%20and%20flood%20the%20company%20with%20cash%20for%20its%20expansion%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20Brown%20could%20sub%20in%20for%20Amodei%20in%20the%20talks%20is%20also%20a%20positive%20sign%20that%20the%20company%20has%20a%20deep%20bench%20of%20empowered%20leaders.%20Brown%20may%20have%20taken%20a%20different%20tone%20than%20his%20boss%2C%20but%20it's%20likely%20he%20had%20many%20of%20the%20same%20points%20to%20make%20%E2%80%94%20last%20year%2C%20Business%20Insider%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-cofounder-tom-brown-career-advice-ai-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Easked%20Brown%3C%2Fa%3E%20what%20advice%20he'd%20give%20for%20people's%20careers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSurround%20yourself%20with%20people%20you%20want%20to%20be%20like%2C%26quot%3B%20Brown%20wrote%20back%2C%20among%20other%20tips.%20%26quot%3BYou'll%20become%20more%20similar%20to%20them%20over%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ECorrection%3A%20July%201%2C%202026%20%E2%80%94%20An%20earlier%20version%20of%20this%20story%20misspelled%20Howard%20Lutnick's%20name.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20a%20tip%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ascouncil%40insider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Escouncil%40insider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20or%20over%20text%2C%20Signal%2C%20Telegram