%20channeled%20through%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20telling%20you%2C%20it%20is%20absolutely%20a%20problem%20for%20this%20country%2C%20because%20we%20are%20on%20the%20cutting%20edge%20of%20every%20single%20AI%20technology%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20if%20you're%20going%20to%20triply%20oversell%20something%20%E2%80%94%20and%20by%20the%20way%2C%20the%20enterprises%20are%20just%20tired%20of%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20asked%20people%20to%20call%20CEOs%20in%20private%20and%20say%3A%20%26quot%3BMad%20man%20Karp%20is%20on%20TV%20saying%20we're%20livid%2C%20I'm%20not%20going%20to%20quote%20you.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20would%20respond%20saying%20they%20are%20%26quot%3Btwice%20as%20livid%26quot%3B%20as%20Karp%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Falexander-karp-criticizes-ai-companies-token-costs-2026-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1782922061000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4521fc2680585ce91a2c3f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Falexander-karp-criticizes-ai-companies-token-costs-2026-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Palantir%20CEO%20Alex%20Karp%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bsomething%20has%20gone%20completely%20wrong%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20AI%20market.%20%26quot%3BThe%20enterprises%20are%20just%20tired%20of%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22hchandonnet%40insider.com%20(Henry%20Chandonnet%2CTom%20Carter)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A94%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2259%20killed%20in%20floods%20and%20fears%20number%20of%20dead%20could%20rise%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1782921900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F26%2F07%2F1920x1080%2Fskynews-ivory-coast-floods_7287426.jpg%3F20260701172313%22%2C%22originID