20alt%3D%5C%22Denise%20Moreno%2C%20left%2C%20and%20Alex%20Schultz%20of%20Meta%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4542982680585ce91a31c5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDenise%20Moreno%20is%20stepping%20into%20Alex%20Schultz's%20CMO%20role%20at%20Meta.%3Cp%3EMeta%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMeta%20is%20getting%20a%20new%20CMO%20in%20a%20C-suite%20shake-up.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDenise%20Moreno%20is%20stepping%20up%20as%20Alex%20Schultz%20becomes%20Meta's%20first%20chief%20data%20officer.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMoreno%20spoke%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20AI%20in%20accelerating%20Meta's%20marketing%20work.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20is%20getting%20a%20new%20CMO.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDenise%20Moreno%20is%20stepping%20into%20the%20role%20as%20Alex%20Schultz%2C%20the%20former%20CMO%2C%20becomes%20Meta's%20first%20chief%20data%20officer%2C%20the%20company%20shared%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMoreno%20has%20had%20a%20lower%20profile%2C%20but%20isn't%20a%20stranger%20to%20the%20top%20job.%20She%20temporarily%20stepped%20into%20the%20CMO%20role%20last%20year%20when%20Schultz%20was%20preparing%20for%20Meta's%20FTC%20trial.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%2017-year%20marketing%20vet%20at%20Meta%2C%20Moreno%20most%20recently%20served%20as%20global%20SVP%20of%20consumer%20marketing%20and%20growth.%20Schultz%20called%20her%20his%20%26quot%3Bquiet%20right%20hand%20on%20growth%2C%26quot%3B%20crediting%20her%20with%20promoting%20Meta's%20products%2C%20including%20its%20AI%20glasses%20and%20Threads%2C%20while%20building%20its%20e-commerce%20capabilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20announcing%20her%20new%20role%2C%20Moreno%20said%20AI%20would%20be%20key%20to%20providing%20scale%20and%20speed%20to%20augment%20the%20company's%20human%20judgment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESchultz%20is%20moving%20into%20the%20data%20officer%20role%20at%20a%20time%20when%20Meta%2C%20along%20with%20other%20tech%20giants%2C%20ramps%20up%20its%20AI%20spending.%20In%20November%2C%20Schultz%20defended%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-cmo-alex-schultz-defends-the-ai-spending-boom-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esector's%20investment%20level%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20Business%20Insider%2C%20saying%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Baggressive%2C%20but%20not%20crazy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20new%20role%2C%20he'll%20focus%20on%20everything%20from%20building%20data%20foundations%20to%20AI-powered%20analytics%2C%20experimentation%2C%20research%2C%20and%20decision-making.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20already%20made%20exciting%20progress%20%E2%80%94%20from%20Analytics%20Agent%2C%20now%20the%20most%20widely%20used%20AI%20agent%20inside%20Meta%2C%20to%20foundational%20work%20modernizing%20our%20analytics%20infrastructure%20%E2%80%94%20but%20I%20believe%20we're%20only%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20what's%20possible%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20on%20LinkedIn.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20Cannes%20Lions%20in%20June%2C%20Schultz%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20an%20interview%20that%20the%20key%20to%20avoiding%20AI%20slop%20is%20the%20same%20as%20avoiding%20bad%20results%20in%20any%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20only%20going%20to%20work%20if%20you%20are%20competent%20at%20using%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20recently%20took%20heat%20for%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frei-backlash-ai-ad-instagram-blamed-meta-ai-tool-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EREI%20ad%3C%2Fa%3E%20made%20with%20a%20Meta%20AI%20tool%20that%20showed%20a%20bike%20with%20two%20sets%20of%20handlebars.%20Meta%20declined%20to%20comment%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20won't%20be%20for%20all%20advertisers%2C%20Schultz%20said%20at%20Cannes%20Lions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20think%20about%20AI%2C%20you're%20going%20to%20have%20three%20categories%20of%20things%20in%20the%20future%2C%20and%20I%20don't%20think%20these%20are%20particularly%20groundbreaking%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20will%20have%20AI-only%20content.%20You%20will%20have%20creators%20who%20are%20enabled%20by%20AI%2C%20and%20you%20will%20have%20people%20and%20advertisers%20who%20swear%20not%20to%20use%20AI.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESchultz%20said%20he%20sees%20AI%20tools%20as%20an%20enabler%20of%20creativity%20and%20analytics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20look%20at%20the%20most%20successful%20people%20in%20analytics%2C%20it's%20the%20ones%20who%20think%20of%20the%20right%20question%20to%20answer%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20by%20the%20way%2C%20they%20can%20use%20the%20AI%20tools%20to%20turbocharge%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ELara%20O'Reilly%20contributed%20reporting.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-names-a-new-cmo-denise-moreno-2026-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1782921279000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-names-a-new-cmo-denise-moreno-2026-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Denise%20Moreno%2C%20a%20marketing%20vet%2C%20is%20stepping%20into%20the%20role%20as%20Alex%20Schultz%20becomes%20Meta's%20first%20chief%20data%20officer.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22lmoses%40insider.com%20(Lucia%20Moses)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A93%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Alia%20Bhatt%20gives%20a%20witty%20comeback%20to%20being%20paid%20for%20IGL%202%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1782921149000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-132118867%2Cimgsize-79913.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fkaun-bola-alia-bhatt-gives-a-witty-comeback-to-being-paid-for-her-appearance-on-samay-rainas-indias-got-latent-2%2Farticleshow%2F132118840.