20at%20Google%3C%2Fa%3E%20helping%20organizations%20implement%20and%20adopt%20AI%20solutions%2C%20yet%20I%20have%20spent%20the%20last%20eight%20years%20raising%20my%20daughter%20with%20nearly%20no%20access%20to%20tech%20beyond%20weekend%20family%20movie%20nights.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20began%20as%20an%20intentional%20decision%2C%20one%20I%20knew%20would%20test%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparent-screen-time-rules-kids-benefited-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elimits%20as%20a%20parent%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20especially%20during%20the%20endless%20%26quot%3BI'm%20bored%26quot%3B%20tantrums%2C%20eventually%20became%20the%20easy%20route.%20I%20would%20bring%20%26quot%3Bmommy's%20bag%20of%20tricks%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20included%20glitter%2C%20games%2C%20and%20glue%2C%20to%20every%20restaurant%20and%20keep%20my%20phone%20strictly%20off%20limits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20glitter-and-glue%20phase%20didn't%20last%20forever.%20As%20she%20gets%20older%2C%20I%20increasingly%20find%20myself%20watching%20her%20peer%20group%20immerse%20themselves%20in%20technology%20and%20worry%20that%20I%20am%20setting%20her%20up%20to%20fall%20behind%20in%20the%20classroom.%20While%20my%20daughter%20has%20briefly%20used%20PowerPoint%2C%20her%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-i-raised-successful-adults-making-education-fun-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eschool%20projects%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20still%20on%20poster%20boards.%20Meanwhile%2C%20her%20friends%20are%20creating%20Canva%20presentations%2C%20videos%2C%20and%20using%20Pinterest%20for%20inspiration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20I%20am%20coming%20to%20terms%20with%20is%20that%20just%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsmartphone-free-childhood-pact-parents-schools-father-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaying%20no%20to%20tech%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20made%20it%20easy%20for%20me%20to%20avoid%20addressing%20the%20reality%20of%20the%20times%20we%20live%20in%20head-on.%20And%20now%2C%20I%20need%20to%20create%20a%20conscious%20plan%20for%20introducing%20technology%20that%20aligns%20with%20our%20family%20values%20and%20what%20I%20think%20is%20important.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c2725072-fcb2-4276-be6e-ae7ab5349dd1%5C%22%3EShe%20told%20me%20to%20ask%20ChatGPT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20as%20I%20sat%20on%20my%20high%20horse%20of%20self-realization%2C%20I%20got%20hit%20with%20another%20dose%20of%20reality.%20We%20were%20on%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-conversations-tween-car-rides-to-school-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecar%20ride%20to%20school%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20catching%20up%20on%20homework%2C%20when%20she%20came%20across%20a%20word%20she%20didn't%20know.%20I%20couldn't%20explain%20what%20the%20word%20meant%2C%20so%20I%20grabbed%20my%20phone%20and%20asked%20ChatGPT%20to%20explain%20it%20to%20an%208-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20got%20the%20answer%20and%20breezed%20through%20her%20exercise%20of%20writing%20a%20sentence%20with%20the%20word.%20This%20is%20normal%20behavior%20for%20me%20these%20days.%20Have%20a%20question%2C%20get%20the%20answer%20immediately.%20No%20big%20deal%2C%20right%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mom%20with%20child%20on%20computer%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a317053e826bfa433d6e7c9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223213%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20wants%20her%20daughter%20to%20coexist%20with%20technology.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20days%20later%2C%20we%20were%20at%20the%20park%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkids-dont-do-homework-family-values-after-school-activities-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edoing%20homework%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20ran%20into%20the%20same%20situation.%20This%20time%2C%20we%20had%20the%20time%20to%20think%20things%20through.%20We%20weren't%20in%20our%20usual%20rush%2C%20and%20I%20wanted%20us%20to%20figure%20this%20out%20together.%20So%20instead%20of%20hitting%20the%20easy%20button%2C%20I%20pushed%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20do%20you%20think%20the%20word%20means%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20know%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20responded.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDoes%20it%20sound%20like%20a%20positive%20or%20negative%20word%3F%26quot%3B%20I%20pressed%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20know.%20Mom%2C%20ugh%2C%20can%20you%20just%20ask%20ChatGPT%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20those%20words%20were%20a%20sucker%20punch.%20Because%20for%20all%20the%20years%20I%20had%20been%20%26quot%3Bshielding%26quot%3B%20her%20from%20technology%2C%20I%20failed%20to%20recognize%20that%20she%20had%20been%20watching%20me%20all%20along.%20Watching%20me%20text%2C%20scroll%2C%20and%20lately%20converse%20with%20AI.%20With%20her%20frustration%20mounting%20and%20her%20eye%20roll%20directed%20at%20me%2C%20she%20was%20mirroring%20my%20own%20behavior%20to%20outsource%20my%20thinking%20in%20a%20pinch.%20But%20I%20kept%20pushing%2C%20her%20memory%20flickered%2C%20and%20she%20found%20the%20answer%20herself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2291b93c52-50a4-424a-8503-ff529fb33fd8%5C%22%3EI%20have%20her%20pause%20and%20reflect%20first%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20moment%20made%20me%20realize%20that%20I%20have%20had%20the%20luxury%20of%20building%20up%20my%20own%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freference%2Fcritical-thinking%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecritical%20thinking%20skills%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20have%20had%20the%20chance%20to%20struggle%20through%20problems%20and%20spend%20endless%20hours%20figuring%20them%20out.%20She%20has%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20tell%20my%20daughter%20it%20is%20OK%20to%20fail%2C%20but%20then%20hand%20her%20the%20AI%20easy%20button%20to%20the%20world's%20information%2C%20I%20am%20taking%20away%20not%20only%20the%20chance%20to%20fail%20but%20also%20the%20chance%20to%20struggle%20and%20learn%20from%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20now%20we%20have%20been%20testing%20out%20some%20rules%2C%20or%20at%20least%20I%20do%2C%20and%20she%20has%20to%20live%20by%20them.%20The%20reality%20is%20that%20we%20need%20to%20learn%20to%20coexist%20with%20technology%20and%20create%20a%20home%20environment%20that%20supports%20our%20kids'%20growth%20in%20and%20out%20of%20the%20classroom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20incorporating%20AI%20into%20the%20mix%2C%20we%20do%20a%20couple%20of%20things.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPause%20and%20reflect%20%E2%80%94%20we%20have%20to%20pause%20and%20give%20ourselves%20time%20to%20imagine%20what%20an%20answer%20could%20be.%20We%20have%20to%20take%20the%20time%20to%20wonder%20or%20solve%20an%20issue%20ourselves.%20We%20play%20and%20come%20up%20with%20impossible%20answers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFact-checking%20game%20%E2%80%94%20we%20will%20look%20up%20a%20video%20or%20article%2C%20trying%20to%20find%20the%20opposite%20answer.%20I%20point%20out%20that%20asking%20questions%20in%20different%20ways%20yields%20different%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAsk%20a%20human%20%E2%80%94%20I%20encourage%20her%20to%20ask%20a%20friend%20or%20family%20member%20what%20they%20think%2C%20and%20to%20get%20curious%20about%20other%20people's%20perspectives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20after%20my%20own%20soul-searching%20into%20my%20values%2C%20I%20have%20come%20to%20believe%20that%20parenting%20in%20the%20age%20of%20AI%20is%20not%20about%20teaching%20your%20little%20one%20how%20to%20use%20the%20tool%20to%20make%20something%20great%20or%20be%20efficient%3B%20they%20will%20get%20that%20eventually.%20It's%20about%20teaching%20your%20little%20one%20to%20still%20think%20for%20themselves%20and%20be%20creative%20with%20their%20thoughts%2C%20within%20a%20system%20that%20makes%20it%20so%20easy%20not%20to.%20It's%20about%20preserving%20the%20small%20inconveniences%20that%20have%20been%20stripped%20away%20by%20same%20day%20delivery%20and%20instant%20answers.%20It%20is%20about%20creating%20space%20for%20intentional%20delayed%20gratification%2C%20for%20agitation%2C%20sighs%2C%20and%20eye%20rolls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-parenting-kids-critical-thinking-2026-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1782921061000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a316b596a1225644000d242%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-parenting-kids-critical-thinking-2026-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Even%20though%20I%20work%20with%20AI%20at%20Google%2C%20I'm%20teaching%20my%20daughter%20to%20pause%2C%20struggle%2C%20and%20think%20before%20turning%20to%20ChatGPT%20for%20answers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Carolaine%20Pino)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22M3M%20Group%20to%20invest%20%E2%82%B910%2C000%20crore%20in%20construction%2C%20land%20acquisition%20in%20FY27%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1782920991000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2025-11%2F05%2Fthumb%2Ffitandfill%2F1200X628%2F1762342894-0653.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fm3m-group-to-invest-10-000-crore-in-construction-land-acquisition-in-fy27-126070101408_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Gurugram-based%20developer%20will%20invest%20Rs%207%2C200%20crore%20in%20construction%20and%20Rs%202%2C500%20crore%20in%20land%20acquisition%20as%20it%20expands%20its%20project%20pipeline%20and%20branded%20housing%20portfolio%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fm3m-group-to-invest-10-000-crore-in-construction-land-acquisition-in-fy27-1260701